 2009-15832009-09-17,  ,  ,  ,  AGRI-FOOD
ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectAgri-Recovery - Alberta Seed Potato Assistance Program
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide assistance through the Agricultural Disaster Relief Program under the AgriRecovery Framework to Alberta seed potato producers affected by the re-closure of the U.S. border due to the discovery of the Potato Cyst Nematode through a contribution under the federal component of the 2009 Alberta Seed Potato Assistance Program.
